snippet.title: The Protagonist: EX-1 | Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
The Protagonist is a story-driven, turn-based, tactical RPG set during the planetary invasion of Terra.

Play as ANGEL, a Terran military operative, and her elite squad, as they infiltrate the alien space station: Ana-Mon.

More information about The Protagonist here: 
https://theprota.com/
